# Stripe Payment Links for the Upgrade modal. Create these in the Stripe Dashboard
# (Payment Links > New) — one per price (Monthly, Yearly, Lifetime). No secret keys
# needed here; Payment Link URLs are public checkout pages.
#
# In each Payment Link's "After payment" settings, set the confirmation redirect to
# this app's deployed URL with `?upgraded=1` appended, e.g.:
#   https://your-quest-log-app.example.com/?upgraded=1
# That's what tells the app the purchase went through.

VITE_STRIPE_LINK_MONTHLY=
VITE_STRIPE_LINK_YEARLY=
VITE_STRIPE_LINK_LIFETIME=
